title: SpaceCraft Noob: Return to Earth
description: SpaceCraft Noob: Return to Earth is a casual adventure game where you become an astronaut and find yourself stranded on an alien planet after a spaceship crash. Your mission? Explore diverse biomes, gather vital resources, and construct advanced factories. Your ultimate goal is to build a rocket and make your way back home. Guide Noob in this cosmic journey filled with challenges and discoveries!
